text: Brianna Wu (born July 6, 1977) is an American video game developer and computer programmer.Brianna Wu, post 7 December 2017. Accessed 13 December 2017. She co-founded Giant Spacekat. Giant Spacekat makes indie games. She is also a blogger and podcaster on matters relating to the video game industry. Wu unsuccessfully ran as a Democrat against incumbent Stephen F. Lynch in Massachusetts for the 8th district for the U.S. House of Representatives in 2018. Wu unsuccessfully ran a second campaign for the 2020 election. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:American artists Category:American political activists Category:Politicians from West Virginia Category:Politicians from Boston
